docs.title: SED Notes and documentation
docs.text: This repository hosts the official documentation for the SED project.

docs.title: Structure
docs.text: The documentation is organized into several main sections, accessible through the navigation bar. Each section corresponds to a folder/topic.

docs.title: Blog
docs.text: This my blog, where I talk about videogames I've played and liked, and film and series that I've enjoyed. Sometimes I'll write about tech stuff too.
